        <p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         <em>
          What\xe2\x80\x99s the first thing founders do when starting a company? Buy a website domain? File incorporation docs? Add \xe2\x80\x9cStealth\xe2\x80\x9d to their LinkedIn?
         </em>
        </p>
        <p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         <em>
          <span>
           Nope. The first thing founders do is start a new
          </span>
          <a href="https://substack.com/redirect/275f06ce-3ea7-4b34-a17e-ba6e6bac8985?j=eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel="" style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">
           Slack Workspace
          </a>
          <span>
           .
          </span>
         </em>
        </p>
        <p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         <em>
          <span>
           Why? Because
          </span>
          <a href="https://substack.com/redirect/275f06ce-3ea7-4b34-a17e-ba6e6bac8985?j=eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel="" style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">
           Slack
          </a>
          <span>
           is where thoughtful work gets done quickly.
          </span>
         </em>
        </p>
        <p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         <em>
          <a href="https://substack.com/redirect/275f06ce-3ea7-4b34-a17e-ba6e6bac8985?j=eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel="" style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); text-decoration: underline;">
           Slack
          </a>
          <span>
           sent us a bunch of ad copy to include here, but this is a product I know and use every single day so I\xe2\x80\x99m going to tell you why I like the product.
          </span>
         </em>
        </p>
        <p style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">
         <em>
          <strong>
           Partner Management.
          </strong>
          <span>
           You know when you have a longstanding partner \xe2\x80\x93 it could be an agency, consultant, supplier \xe2\x80\x93 and you have dozens of poorly labeled emails threads going with them? Yeah, just skip all of that and get your closest partners added to your Slack channel, either as a member or via Connect.
          </span>
         </em>
