           <em>
            <a href="https://substack.com/redirect/44943231-8c28-4178-8843-c7a986a8b84c?j=eyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU" rel="" style="text-decoration: underline;">
